# Projex AI Architecture

## Overview

Projex AI follows a simple client-side architecture designed for rapid prototyping and proof-of-concept development.

The application captures project requirements, evaluates team capabilities, and generates AI-powered project planning recommendations.

## Architecture Flow

User Input
↓
Team Registry
↓
Client Brief Collection
↓
Project Analysis
↓
AI Planning Engine
↓
Project Recommendations
↓
Output Dashboard

## Core Modules

### Team Registry Module

Stores:

* Team Members
* Skills
* Roles
* Experience Levels

Purpose:

* Resource selection
* Team recommendations

### Client Brief Module

Captures:

* Project Name
* Requirements
* Industry
* Budget
* Constraints
* Priority

Purpose:

* Define project objectives

### AI Planning Module

Generates:

* Executive Summary
* Methodology Recommendations
* Team Allocation
* Timeline Planning
* Risk Register
* KPIs

### Project Repository

Stores project plans using browser local storage.

